          <title>Lehkonen gets hat trick as Colorado beats Utah, 4-1</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - Utah's struggles on its home ice continue. Artturi Lehkonen scored his first NHL hat trick, and the Colorado Avalanche won 4-1 against the Utah Hockey Club at Delta Center in Salt Lake City on Friday. Utah lost all three games on this current homestand.]]></description>
