        <item>
          <title>Latvia stuns Canada in world junior hockey, winning 3-2 on lone shootout goal</title>
          <description><![CDATA[OTTAWA, Ontario (AP) — Eriks Mateiko scored the lone goal of a shootout in the eighth round to give Latvia a 3-2 victory over Canada on Friday night in the world junior hockey championship.]]></description>
